    <item>
      <title>最高法院支持 1 月 6 日被告，限制安然法律的使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/supreme-court-backs-jan-6-defendant-curbing-use-of-enron-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院支持 1 月 6 日国会骚乱被告的裁决，该裁决可能影响数百起起诉，其中包括华盛顿针对前总统唐纳德·特朗普的刑事案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/supreme-court-backs-jan-6-defendant-curbing-use-of-enron-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 14:49:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院推翻雪佛龙规则，打击代理权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/supreme-court-overturns-chevron-ruling-in-blow-to-agency-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院意见分歧，推翻了已有数十年历史的法律原则，该原则授权联邦监管机构解释不明确的法律，并发布了一项重磅裁决，将对环境、消费者和金融监管机构形成约束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/supreme-court-overturns-chevron-ruling-in-blow-to-agency-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 14:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒙古执政党赢得议会多数席位但失利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/mongolians-head-to-polls-for-country-s-biggest-ever-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙古执政党在周五的议会选举中以微弱优势赢得多数席位，但由于选民要求打击腐败并更多地利用该国的矿产资源，该党落后于反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/mongolians-head-to-polls-for-country-s-biggest-ever-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
